subject: Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: The teenager Graham Rahal overcame a spinout and came back to win the Honda Grand Prix of St. Petersburg on Sunday in Florida, holding off the veteran Hélio Castroneves to become the youngest winner in major open-wheel history.
